        and then reduce it modulo ``modulus``.

        .. SEEALSO::

            :meth:`~sage.rings.polynomial.skew_polynomial_element._pow_`

        EXAMPLES::

            sage: k.<t> = GF(5^3)
            sage: Frob = k.frobenius_endomorphism()
